description: Try this easy chicken tikka masala recipe with pumpkin. It’s ready in 20 minutes but will taste like you’ve been cooking for hours.
keywords: Tikka masala,Seafood free,Egg free,Winter,Pumpkin,Quick & easy dinner,Microwave,Wheat free,Rice,Chicken,Dinner Made Easy
name: 20-Minute Chicken & Pumpkin Tikka Masala Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 2 cup Prep Set Go pumpkin chunks
450g SunRice steamed basmati fragrant white rice
300g The Spice Tailor original tikka masala

recipeInstructions.text: Place pumpkin in a microwave-safe bowl, cover, then microwave on high for 2 minutes or until thawed. Drain.
Heat rice according to packet instructions.

Meanwhile, heat oil in a large, deep frying pan over medium-high heat. Add spices from masala packet and cook for 20 seconds or until fragrant. Add chicken and cook for 3 minutes or until browned. Add base sauce from masala packet. Reduce heat to medium, then simmer for 2 minutes or until fragrant.
Add main sauce from masala packet and pumpkin. Simmer for a further 6 minutes, stirring occasionally, or until chicken is cooked through. Serve curry over rice.
